content: It doesn't let me to export or backup my data. It keeps crashing. Support doesn't respond.

Нельзя импортнуть базу!!! Купил это сперва на iOS, все ок, было. Перешёл на андроид, так же купил в надежде перенести базу с Айфона, зря деньги потратил, такой возможности тупо нет. Что за прикол такой?
This went from being the best tracker to the absolute worst. I paid for the service. Now it doesn't work. I want a refund. Do not download
Abandoned app, no support, can't backup data

Haven't used this app in literally about 6 months. The "bankroll" feature doesn't work, so you cannot edit a bankroll. Worse than that, it won't let me put in completed sessions anymore. As soon as I enter a number in buy-in, it goes back to main screen. No Twitter support, their last respond was 2017. DO NOT BUY
Horrible. Paid version. Zero support. Abandoned app. No longer supported. Falsely claims can back up. Stay away!
I've been using this almost a decade, it's worked great up until recently and will no longer back up and the dev's do not respond.
Program worked great for 4 years. Now I can't get it to backup anymore. Support won't email me back.
You can't login to the app and you lose your data
Underwhelming overall with too many crashes. IMO not a useable application. If it was possible the rating would be zero stars.
Terrible no support at at, doesnt answer emails I paid for the app and it has problems cannot backup would not recommend to anyone

As a professional player, this is what I use on a daily basis for several years now. It's a good program however the developer has stopped responding to bug reports. The data export no longer works. After 9 years using this I've finally uninstalled and now using a different one. glad i made the switch
can't backup data app keeps on crashing. support also doesn't exist or respond to emails. apps given up
keeps crashing when I put a bankroll total in
The account settings haven't worked since android pie was introduced
It would be nice if this developer app had the question you asked support team
keep crush when backup data.
Cannot export or backup data and cannot register as user. Both options not working, and no response to my questions.
All support doesn't work so your data is lost.
I can't transfer data from my old device to my new device.  I've emailed their support 3 times and didn't get a response.
Great for keeping track of both tournaments and cash games. Great stats for everything.
Falsely promises to save your data. I have just upgraded my Android and discovered my data is all stranded on my old phone.

Downloaded after switching from iOS to Android with the impression I could easily import my data from poker tracker. After following the very vague instructions and trying multiple times I was unsuccessful. Emailed support twice, messaged them on Facebook and after more than a week radio silence. I would stay away

As of recently I cannot backup my data.  It always errors out at 30% of the backup.  I have sent multiple emails and have gotten no response.   Totally satisfied with the product but will need to switch to a new tracker if I cannot backup the data

Great app with glitches. u get a standard bankroll option named default with 2 locations attached to it.You can not delete any bankroll unless you delete the locations attached first.Somtimes the location will appear in bankroll after deleteing location making it impossible to delete the br. Also if u delete the default bankroll and make a new one with dif name it will bring back default again changing location info 2 default and if u delete locations it can say they r still attached with no way to delete.   Edit they fixed glitching.
Great app only needs to improve its graphs
Excellent app!
Poker Income
Perfect
Have year worth of data backed up on  app / site and it will not restore. (Same model phone.) I get no response from support. Paid version.
By far the easy program to jump into to use
I can't create an account to back up my data. It tells me error loading page please fix this.
There are things that could be improved on, but since no other poker tracking app even comes close to this one. It gets five stars
Easy to use
Best
It choses when to log my sessions. It often doesn't let you scroll down past half way. I'm super disappointed I paid for it. Definitely NOT for professional players!
app works great only problem is I can't put multiple currencies in at once.  for example I play in Australia and america i want it to track for both currencies
Love the app.. its extremely  helpful
I particularly like the online backup and restore - when I lost my phone I didn't lose years of data.

A routine is how you progress at everything. This app let's me track my progress in every area of the game. The app helps me analyse and work on my weak areas. If you want to get better at poker, it's a must have . Here it is 2 years  later and I  basically  feel  the same.  Just wish there was a way to back up information.
Very good app. It's missing a filter for best and worst sessions
Every time I attempt to back up now the app crashes. Now I'll have no way to transfer my data when I change phones. Where's support?
Since the update I cant log my recent session
1 thing its needs. It needs to keep my data saved in the cloud so I can access it when I change devices

Good for the "good" rec.players Always lost all data anytime I upgraded my phone plus all the foremention glitches I grad. stopped using this app Playing for a living, your bookkeeping needs to be on point as you are also paying for a living (rake/tip) I use color notes "syncedalways" created a simple template (datetimelocationstakes etc) Monthly,I transfer to a masterspreadsheet on pc, my results are never lost. You can create the same dataanalysis on spreadsheet. Overall, playing for keeps, I pass.
Emailed support about this and no reply.  I have an S5 running the latest Lollipop.  Please fix manage data error.

Great app. Offers pretty much every feature you need to break down and review your results. The only issue I've had is that some of the charts don't display correctly on my Galaxy S4. If not for that minor bug this app would be an easy 5 stars. Even so, really satisfied with my purchase.

Lost a years worth of records. Not able to recover. Not able to a response from support. The first time I switched devices the data automatically updated and restored. I had to switch devices again and now hundreds of sessions and records are gone. Support will not respond. Records are a vital part of playing poker. This app is unreliable and should not be used as there is no support. My backup files will not load.
Excellent app.
Simple  to use. Good charts. Good game reports.
Nuff said
Been through a few apps,  like this one the best
Best poker session tracker out there!
great

Best bankroll management app.
Poker tracker

App

This app is totally hopeless. Everytime I do anything I get an error message. When I am able to put stuff in, sometimes it registers sometimes it doesn't. Big waste of money. Go with something else cause it can't be as bad as this

Trash, don't buy.  It deletes info.  Very confusing. Buyer be ware
This app single handedly prevented me from switching to a windows phone. Love this app.
Best tracking software for pokerz
Awesome app.. great for keeping your bankroll in check....developer fixed issues I was having fast...I recommend this to everyone

Cant log into pokerincome website, unresponsive customer support. After many emails and twitter requests.  You're lucky i hate poker agent or i would pay them less money for a better product.    Pretty sure the designer abandoned this app.

Everything is good but the only problem I got is the hourly rate. They round up which they say to simplify. That really don't make any sense. How can u accurately know ur Hrly rate that way. If u play for 1.5 hrs it will say 2hrs. Poker log is much better & financito to keep track of my bankroll. Hopefully they fix this!

Have had this app on iphone and now droid. App is good until u run into update glitches which has wiped out most of my data even after backing up to their server. Tech support is almost non existent. So over time app is pretty useless if unstable to track your data.
Best on market. The GUI isn't the prettiest, will upgrade to 5* if the graphs/gui look nicer in a future uograde. Nice work Dev!

Great app but I just upgraded to a Nexus and a Galaxy and I can't use it.

Often force close when opening on droid classic.
I rate excellent because this software is great at tracking your bankroll etc. Also the BEST customer service I have seen in a while frm SW developer
Great program. Keep up the good work and please continue to update. I really like it.
